 *  - SH_QUIZ_ITEMS:      teacher_quiz_items
 *
 * Key notes:
 *  - access_code is generated at create and unique across ALL quizzes.
 *  - custom_fields_json is teacher-defined schema (max 4 fields). Minimal validation only.
 *  - Publishing creates IMMUTABLE snapshots in teacher_quiz_items and flips quiz to PUBLISHED.
 *  - Publish supports:
 *      (a) bank references: { bank_item_id, marks? }
 *      (b) inline items:    { inline: { stem, option_a..f, correct, ... }, marks? }
 *    Inline items are auto-saved into teacher_bank_items with source_type="QUIZ_INLINE".
